{"tid":314250,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"諗住9月中去台北,有咩好介紹?","createTime":"2017-07-09T04:31:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-18T11:55:05.000Z","uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"41d5e6f22b1f7b83168b6e00224072f462bbdad7","tid":314250,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T04:31:23.000Z","msg":"之前同屋企人第一次去台灣,感覺幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗住9月中再去多次<br />\n暫時plan定去4日<br />\nDay 1: 到酒店先休息下,夜晚去西門町(之前去係朝早,完全冇野睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\nDay 2: 想去下台北出名D博物館OR文青地方<br />\nDay 3: 去宜蘭玩一日,夜晚返台北<br />\nDay 4: 朝早check out,行一陣,最後返香港<br />\n<br />\n我依家煩梗既係Day 2有咩地方值得去<br />\n之前有人話故宮博物院悶到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問下各位台北有咩博物館OR文青地方係值得去?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"641683976adcb2a28054955277fbee54d2bc4e6d","tid":314250,"uid":84998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T04:32:21.000Z","msg":"去叫雞"},{"pid":"980bbe80dbd01def3f17b217c2113b92baa82b61","tid":314250,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T04:32:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去叫雞</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b20863d24b41863433532d4a790837d00150062","tid":314250,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T04:33:35.000Z","msg":"華山文創園區囉，文精必去"},{"pid":"1bdfce2e05d75a870a864252146f2fb6f08ddab8","tid":314250,"uid":73907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T04:35:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前同屋企人第一次去台灣,感覺幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗住9月中再去多次<br />\n暫時plan定去4日<br />\nDay 1: 到酒店先休息下,夜晚去西門町(之前去係朝早,完全冇野睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\nDay 2: 想去下台北出名D博物館OR文青地方<br />\nDay 3: 去宜蘭玩一日,夜晚返台北<br />\nDay 4: 朝早check out,行一陣,最後返香港<br />\n<br />\n我依家煩梗既係Day 2有咩地方值得去<br />\n之前有人話故宮博物院悶到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問下各位台北有咩博物館OR文青地方係值得去?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去 蔣介石/孫中山個博物館囉 再唔係去誠品個旗艦店 我記得附近有啲藝術/創意社區 設計味幾濃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c00af3481c277a2b13be84ae871af987b7b4884","tid":314250,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T04:37:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>之前同屋企人第一次去台灣,感覺幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗住9月中再去多次<br />\n暫時plan定去4日<br />\nDay 1: 到酒店先休息下,夜晚去西門町(之前去係朝早,完全冇野睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\nDay 2: 想去下台北出名D博物館OR文青地方<br />\nDay 3: 去宜蘭玩一日,夜晚返台北<br />\nDay 4: 朝早check out,行一陣,最後返香港<br />\n<br />\n我依家煩梗既係Day 2有咩地方值得去<br />\n之前有人話故宮博物院悶到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問下各位台北有咩博物館OR文青地方係值得去?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去 蔣介石/孫中山個博物館囉 再唔係去誠品個旗艦店 我記得附近有啲藝術/創意社區 設計味幾濃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中正紀念堂之前去過<br />\n誠品旗艦店=松山文創區?"},{"pid":"0780f0753fd0251c7d1030f7d5a88d9c95aeab8d","tid":314250,"uid":44550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T04:44:48.000Z","msg":"宜蘭太多嘢可以做  一日邊夠"},{"pid":"812551af54eda9d9904d6bc5d2d101b805c096be","tid":314250,"uid":84998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T04:45:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去叫雞</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你台妹咁正唔係唔試下呀嘛"},{"pid":"f309adb4c6fd164290112c995eaeeb167e6a93ca","tid":314250,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T04:45:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n之前有人話故宮博物院悶到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問下各位台北有咩博物館OR文青地方係值得去?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知你要邊類型先會唔悶<br />\n因為台灣各地都有唔少博物館/紀念館<br />\n<br />\n文青地方好多<br />\n例如上面巴打講既華山/1914<br />\n我覺得例如有些在商業區旁的小社區<br />\n大學區附近咁<br />\n以至一間小cafe<br />\n我諗都算係卦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"360324b91305287df37731ba56bb5f8d218e1117","tid":314250,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T04:46:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去叫雞</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你台妹咁正唔係唔試下呀嘛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6e9cfbe74f4e21f0b44282d86e36b6ceb8fa686","tid":314250,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T04:49:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>宜蘭太多嘢可以做  一日邊夠</blockquote><br />\n其實個到只有一個景點想去<br />\n所以一日就得"},{"pid":"e6ab8fa2d55e333ae762496c7fdcb7c61d2ec1b7","tid":314250,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T04:54:48.000Z","msg":"同埋順便問下<br />\n西門町有咩一定要食OR一定要玩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"588bbc101591ebad0029af944c9ca4fe9a1d4198","tid":314250,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T04:57:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同埋順便問下<br />\n西門町有咩一定要食OR一定要玩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去&ldquo;三兄妹&ldquo;食冰<br />\n帶定筆去留名，反攻韓狗<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">（該店牆身可以任寫）</span>"},{"pid":"0f9fd5011cb7ae9978b7c6fbd0a6ee8054ecdcf1","tid":314250,"uid":55113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T05:01:45.000Z","msg":"幾多個人<br />\n4-5人可以包車一日遊"},{"pid":"91de38d0841a02bebd80fdb3411cc3784141b3d5","tid":314250,"uid":73907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T05:01:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同埋順便問下<br />\n西門町有咩一定要食OR一定要玩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有間賣苦瓜茶 好撚多人排隊 幾好飲 唔好排錯 有兩間連埋一齊 但其中一間勁拍烏蠅"},{"pid":"9e2a1e3d792199792cd575efd01ab654886be977","tid":314250,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T05:02:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同埋順便問下<br />\n西門町有咩一定要食OR一定要玩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有間賣苦瓜茶 好撚多人排隊 幾好飲 唔好排錯 有兩間連埋一齊 但其中一間勁拍烏蠅</blockquote><br />\n名唔該?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96eb8a8dce2d0aa7ec0f0f74c03265c7d0